[i]Version 2.0.0[/i]
[h2]Lead Sight Revamped - Takeover & Maintenance Update[/h2]

This update officially rebrands the "Rifted Lead Sight" re-upload as [b]Lead Sight Revamped[/b]. I have officially taken over full development and maintenance of this mod to keep it alive for current versions of Avorion, with full credit to [b]SigmatroN[/b] as the original author. 

[b]Highlights & Fixes:[/b]
[list]
[*]Added modernization-focused stability guards for current Avorion behavior.[/*]
[*]Preserved and integrated the critical hotfix provided by SigmatroN to prevent laser buzzing and crash side-effects ([i]newEffect.soundMaxRadius = 0[/i] and [i]newEffect.soundVolume = 0[/i]).[/*]
[*]Improved reticle effect safety handling during rapid sector/runtime transitions.[/*]
[*]Added configurable script options for easier user maintenance:
  [list]
  [*]Toggle key binding variable[/*]
  [*]Chat feedback toggle[/*]
  [*]Sound feedback toggle[/*]
  [*]Debug logging toggle[/*]
  [/list][/*]
[/list]

[b]Behavior Notes:[/b]
[list]
[*]Core lead prediction behavior remains faithful to the original mod intent.[/*]
[*]Projectile-only averaging logic remains in place (beams and seekers are excluded).[/*]
[*]Default toggle remains [b]/[/b] (slash key), now backed by configurable constants in the script.[/*]
[/list]

[i]Recommended Subscriber Note:[/i] If anything behaves unexpectedly on specific Avorion branches or in multiplayer-heavy sectors, please report the issue with your Avorion version, SP/MP mode, weapon setup, and whether the issue occurs consistently after a sector reload.